SeedCTL is a command-line tool for generating cryptocurrency wallet
seeds using user-provided entropy sources.

Important Notice

SeedCTL handles cryptographic material including mnemonic phrases
and private keys.

SeedCTL does not store, transmit, or recover private keys.

Users are solely responsible for securely storing their mnemonic
phrases and private keys.

Loss or exposure of these secrets may result in permanent loss of
cryptocurrency funds.
